  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Mow catnip. Unlock furr. Hang out.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/0a8702e7df51bc015b266fd884f26e75.poster.avif?t=1771522616\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/0a8702e7df51bc015b266fd884f26e75.webm?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/0a8702e7df51bc015b266fd884f26e75.mp4?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Mow Meow, where you're a stretchy, slightly broken cat with one job — mow catnip. As you gather more catnip, you'll unlock fresh furr and eventually collars, boots, and hats to style your feline. Work alone or team up with friends in this multiplayer sandbox where the only rule is... keep mowing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/603d935c2cf09969b48889a705d326c0.poster.avif?t=1771522616\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/603d935c2cf09969b48889a705d326c0.webm?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/603d935c2cf09969b48889a705d326c0.mp4?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your kitty, embrace the weird, and discover unexpected upgrades as you spiral deeper into this world of fuzzy chaos. The catnip never stops growing — and neither do the surprises. 🤯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Online multiplayer catnip mowing with friends or strangers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Chill original music to soundtrack your feline journey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Unlockable furr [eventually hats, collars, shoes, and other mysterious broken upgrades too]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Strange, buggy ragdoll low-gravity kitty controls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Relaxing yet strangely addictive gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• A world where cats rule, catnip never runs out, and oddities are a feature, not a bug</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/5254f422a01cef8acd68d72de34ee5e8.poster.avif?t=1771522616\" width=320 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/5254f422a01cef8acd68d72de34ee5e8.webm?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/5254f422a01cef8acd68d72de34ee5e8.mp4?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong><i>Mow together. Gather together. Stay weird together.</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Mow catnip. Unlock furr. Hang out.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/0a8702e7df51bc015b266fd884f26e75.poster.avif?t=1771522616\" width=400 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/0a8702e7df51bc015b266fd884f26e75.webm?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/0a8702e7df51bc015b266fd884f26e75.mp4?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Mow Meow, where you're a stretchy, slightly broken cat with one job — mow catnip. As you gather more catnip, you'll unlock fresh furr and eventually collars, boots, and hats to style your feline. Work alone or team up with friends in this multiplayer sandbox where the only rule is... keep mowing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/603d935c2cf09969b48889a705d326c0.poster.avif?t=1771522616\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/603d935c2cf09969b48889a705d326c0.webm?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/603d935c2cf09969b48889a705d326c0.mp4?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your kitty, embrace the weird, and discover unexpected upgrades as you spiral deeper into this world of fuzzy chaos. The catnip never stops growing — and neither do the surprises. 🤯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Online multiplayer catnip mowing with friends or strangers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Chill original music to soundtrack your feline journey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Unlockable furr [eventually hats, collars, shoes, and other mysterious broken upgrades too]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Strange, buggy ragdoll low-gravity kitty controls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• Relaxing yet strangely addictive gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\t• A world where cats rule, catnip never runs out, and oddities are a feature, not a bug</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/5254f422a01cef8acd68d72de34ee5e8.poster.avif?t=1771522616\" width=320 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/5254f422a01cef8acd68d72de34ee5e8.webm?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3529400/extras/5254f422a01cef8acd68d72de34ee5e8.mp4?t=1771522616\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><strong><i>Mow together. Gather together. Stay weird together.</i></strong></p>",
